    <h3>Overview</h3>

    <p>
      Political Science              : The effect of regional and provincial culture on the operation of political parties and the institutions of government; the effect of institutional modernization on provincial governments; the role of provincial sub-systems within the Canadian political system.          </p>

    <p class="catalog-terms">
